Interface IInteractiveElement

  • All Superinterfaces:
    IElement, IReadableElement
    All Known Subinterfaces:
    IButton, ICalendar, ICheckBox, IDropDown, IEditableElement, IHyperLink, IImage, IInteractiveTable, IRadioGroup, ISelectList, ITable, ITextField
    All Known Implementing Classes:
    Button, CheckBox, DropDown, HyperLink, Image, Input, InteractiveElement, RadioGroup, Select, Table

    public interface IInteractiveElement
extends IReadableElement
    Base interface for all elements that user can interact with (click, type, check, etc)
